<item>
            <title>[DERBY-6242] Merge ConcurrentXactFactory into XactFactory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6242</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ConcurrentXactFactory extends XactFactory and replaces XactFactory&apos;s Hashtable with a ConcurrentHashMap for better scalability.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now that ConcurrentHashMap is available on all platforms supported on trunk, we could make XactFactory use a ConcurrentHashMap and remove ConcurrentXactFactory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
